name: Madanbhandari project
tagline: Development of an online Learning Management System(LMS) for Madan Bhandari Memorial College.
body:
### Welcome to Madan Bhandari LMS Project.
This project is a development of an online Learning Management System for Madan Bhandari Memorial College. This project was chosen for FYP in BSc(Hons.) in Computing of Islington College.  

The project is underconstruction. 

___
